Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:51.13,Main,,0,0,0,,We hated you from the beginning--\Nand loved you from the beginning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:56.77,Main,,0,0,0,,And so we wanted to become true\Nfriends with you. To cross the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:03.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Defendant-bear Lulu Yurigasaki, I ask you:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:08.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you give up on love?\NOr will you give up on kisses?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:10.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't give up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:12.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll give up on kisses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.03,0:01:19.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. Please make me a human girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:24.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I really want to go to the\Nother side of the wall with Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:29.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikumaaaaaaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:30.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:37.60,Main,,0,0,0,,"I CAN'T GET A KISS"\N{\i1}Viens avec moi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:40.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Church chimes echo in the distance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:43.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Offer up a prayer and betray today{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:49.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wander in a dark forest, then become{\i0}\N{\i1}the morning moon at the Wall of Severance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:51.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't join the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.82,0:01:55.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once I've made you stickier{\i0}\N{\i1}with sweet, thin honey{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:59.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, approve me, I'll be a good girl{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:05.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Picture-book pages dancing on{\i0}\N{\i1}the breeze shake up shadowy memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:17.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be waiting you-know-where,{\i0}\N{\i1}in an empty world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:22.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if everything falls apart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you have to gracefully writhe,{\i0}\N{\i1}even if you have to bend space-time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:33.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Find me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:44.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flower petals will slowly{\i0}\N{\i1}enfold us on a starry night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:46.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:48.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:51.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
