Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:15.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Severance Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:15.82,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Severance Court・(Place)"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:21.08,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Come, the door has opened.\NThis is the land of enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:25.08,Main,,0,0,0,,for all living things...\Nyes, even human and bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.37,MainTop,,0,0,0,,I am LIFE Sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:29.54,MainTop,,0,0,0,,I am LIFE Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:33.42,MainTop,,0,0,0,,I am LIFE Beauty. Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:36.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, since court is not in session today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:41.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I would tell you all a useful story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:46.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Honor! We're not spending\Ntoday looking like this, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:50.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm just too cute! Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:52.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not very cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:56.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You're cute, Cool. Not as cute as {\i1}me{\i0}, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:57.70,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Order!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:05.20,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"The Princess Who Gave Up on Kisses"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.75,Main,,0,0,0,,"The Princess Who Gave Up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:09.62,Main,,0,0,0,,...on Kisses"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:15.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, shall we begin? That's the sexy way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:17.26,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Shaba-da-doo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:27.56,Main,,0,0,0,,before the Wall of Severance\Nseparated people and bears,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,there was a bear kingdom in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,And in that kingdom, there lived a\Nvery beautiful princess named Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Princess Lulu was the heir to\Nthe throne--the future queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:50.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Princess Lulu was special\Nfrom the moment she was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Not a day went by
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:56.71,Main,,0,0,0,,without the bears of the castle\Npraising her charm and beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.59,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"12 Years Ago, Lulu, Age 4・(History)"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:01.88,Main,,0,0,0,,How adorable you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:05.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Princess Lulu, you are our\Nkingdom's greatest treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:10.06,Main,,0,0,0,,No pearl or gem can outshine Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:15.56,Main,,0,0,0,,We're truly blessed to serve\Nsuch a beautiful princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.78,Main,,0,0,0,,So blessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:30.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, Princess Lulu was the\Nfavorite of all the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:32.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:34.79,Main,,0,0,0,,And then, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:39.84,MainTop,,0,0,0,,More shooting stars fell to earth\Nthan anyone had ever seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:45.97,Main,,0,0,0,,They were fragments of Kumaria,\Nfrom the far reaches of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:55.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Princess, rejoice! Her Majesty\Nhas just given birth to a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:59.15,MainTop,,0,0,0,,You have a new baby brother, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:03.65,MainTop,,0,0,0,,The king and queen are both\Nbeside themselves with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:09.29,MainTop,,0,0,0,,The long-awaited prince...\NNow our kingdom is secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:13.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Then... who's the heir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:14.58,Main,,0,0,0,,The prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:17.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Excuse {\i0}me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:22.67,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Shaba-daa... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:25.84,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Shaba-daba-daabaa... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:30.56,Main,,0,0,0,,From that day forward, Princess Lulu\Nwas no longer the favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.35,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Several Years Later・(History)"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:40.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Prince Milne!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:42.90,Main,,0,0,0,,How adorable you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:47.03,Main,,0,0,0,,We're so blessed to serve such a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,From the moment her brother was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:58.46,Main,,0,0,0,,the entire castle--no, the entire kingdom--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:02.00,Main,,0,0,0,,was wild about the little prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:06.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu, the princess, was unwanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:16.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:22.07,Main,,0,0,0,,--Sis!\N--That kid is in the way! Big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:32.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey Sis, is it true that "real love" turns into stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:37.75,Main,,0,0,0,,See, Mommy reads me a picture book every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:44.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Does it really turn into stars? Does it? Does it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:45.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:49.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Real love climbs up to heaven\Nand turns into stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:52.56,Main,,0,0,0,,A shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:59.60,Main,,0,0,0,,And when a shooting star falls to earth,\Nit turns into a Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:03.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Ha! Love turning into a kiss?\NWhat a stupid fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:05.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Such a turn-off, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:10.95,Main,,0,0,0,,So Promise Kisses must be all\Nsparkly and colored like stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:19.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, then I'll go get the\NPromise Kiss for you, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:22.50,Main,,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--I love you lots,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:25.92,Main,,0,0,0,,so that shooting star was my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:28.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be on the ground somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.52,Main,,0,0,0,,But at that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:46.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Princess Lulu realized just how she could\Nget rid of her pesky little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:48.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Desire...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:49.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Bear shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:55.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Milne. Do you love your big sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:58.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep! I love you! Kiss me, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:01.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I will, if you bring me a Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:02.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:04.84,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, better get in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:09.26,Main,,0,0,0,,"Love"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:10.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Die! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:24.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Desire. Now {\i1}I {\i0}can be the favorite again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:33.32,Main,,0,0,0,,The world will start wanting me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.41,Main,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:37.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm home, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:42.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Prince Milne, whom she'd\Nassumed was dead, came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:43.42,Main,,0,0,0,,And what's more...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:47.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, your Promise Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:52.26,Main,,0,0,0,,It's sparkly and the same color as a star, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:55.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-This is just honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:59.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Now you gotta give me a kiss. You promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:02.89,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you promised! Kiss me! Kiss me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:05.90,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Sis, kiss me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:09.78,Main,,0,0,0,,He bugs me, bugs me, bugs me--{\i1}bug off{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:13.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Princess Lulu threw away
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:17.58,Main,,0,0,0,,the Promise Kiss that\NPrince Milne had brought her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:22.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Because it wasn't what she'd wanted at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:30.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Milne. Do you love your big sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:34.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep! I love you! Kiss me, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:37.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I will, if you bring me a Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:40.35,Main,,0,0,0,,--Okay!\N--All right, better get in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:41.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:44.69,Main,,0,0,0,,"Love"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:46.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,"Love"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:06.17,Main,,0,0,0,,This time I'm getting my desire for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:11.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Now you gotta give me a kiss.\NYou promised. C'mon--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:14.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Bugs me, bugs me--{\i1}bug off{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:19.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Milne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.43,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Skipping Forward・(History)"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:24.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep! I love you! Kiss me, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:38.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This {\i0}time, desire max!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:42.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Now you gotta give me a kiss. You promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:43.70,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, kiss me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:48.63,Main,,0,0,0,,no matter how many times\Nshe sent him plummeting to his death,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:54.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Prince Milne returned to\NPrincess Lulu time and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:59.01,Main,,0,0,0,,In his small hands, he would have\Nthe Promise Kiss--that pot of honey,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:01.43,Main,,0,0,0,,and with a smile, he would pester her for a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:05.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Bugs me, bugs me--{\i1}bug off{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:11.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Until one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:13.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I have terrible news!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:20.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Prince Milne has passed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:22.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I saw it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:25.58,Main,,0,0,0,,It was a complete accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.21,Main,,0,0,0,,An accidental death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:34.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, it worked out the way I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:40.34,Main,,0,0,0,,And so Princess Lulu became\Nthe kingdom's favorite once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:56.23,Main,,0,0,0,,That dream again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:13:00.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Simmer, porridge, simmer softly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:02.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:05.45,Main,,0,0,0,,And for the finishing touch, my special...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a dream.\NI killed Yurizono by my own hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.75,Main,,0,0,0,,A bear turned human...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.38,Main,,0,0,0,,But why? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurigasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:23.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you, call me Lulu... Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:24.55,Main,,0,0,0,,"Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:27.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! You're Kureha, so "Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}" works!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:30.77,Main,,0,0,0,,It's cute, right? I'm so clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:34.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Never mind. How did you get into my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:38.65,Main,,0,0,0,,The window was open.\NOr more like broken, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:43.82,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you after? You come\Ninto my house without permission,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.41,Main,,0,0,0,,and then start {\i1}cooking{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:47.91,Main,,0,0,0,,There's only so much meddling I can stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:52.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl... We came to see if you were okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:56.09,Main,,0,0,0,,You haven't come to school\Nsince it happened, Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:58.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yuriika knows where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.47,Main,,0,0,0,,But we were worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:06.97,Main,,0,0,0,,"Worried"? Drop the act. I'm sure\Nyou're invisible like the others by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:12.60,Main,,0,0,0,,No, we're your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:18.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep. Here, a Lulu special! It's honey porridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:21.95,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so tasty, it'll make\Nyou all growly-gooey inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:24.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:26.45,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:31.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's share it, Miss Big Eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:34.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Food does taste better eaten together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:36.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika is my only friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:45.55,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Flitting to About a Year Ago・(History)"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:50.06,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Several years had passed\Nsince Prince Milne died,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:52.73,Main,,0,0,0,,and Princess Lulu became\Nthe kingdom's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:55.69,Main,,0,0,0,,She had grown into a beautiful lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:15:00.32,Main,,0,0,0,,and prince after prince visited from\Nsurrounding kingdoms. Each time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:05.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Princess, give me a Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:09.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I want a romance with you\Nthat burns hotter than the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:12.00,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the sexy way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Shaba-da-doo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:21.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, you mustn't be\Ntaken in by playbears like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:24.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Were {\i1}I {\i0}to receive your Promise Kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:29.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I would double your kingdom's\Neconomy--nay, increase it tenfold!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:31.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:35.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:38.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You're both fools, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:42.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Cuteness is what really\Nmatters in a man! Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll stay by your side forever, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:50.12,Main,,0,0,0,,So give me a Promise Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:53.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:56.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:58.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you get the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:03.88,Main,,0,0,0,,The attention of her people,\Nauthority, words of love:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:07.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Princess Lulu had gotten\Neverything she wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:12.01,Main,,0,0,0,,It was all thanks to\NPrince Milne's convenient death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:16.68,Main,,0,0,0,,And yet, she never felt happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.73,Main,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:22.61,Main,,0,0,0,,...plagued by an awful feeling of emptiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.78,Main,,0,0,0,,as though she had mislaid\Nsomething deeply precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.91,Main,,0,0,0,,And then, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:36.25,Main,,0,0,0,,What? If it's more new dresses\Nor princes, I don't want them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:40.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Milne...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:46.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm home, Sis. Here, your Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:50.97,Main,,0,0,0,,How far did you go looking for that, Milne?\NEveryone thinks you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:57.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Super far away. It was really,\Nreally hard, but I finally made it home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:17:00.98,Main,,0,0,0,,But if I take it, I know\NI'll just throw it away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:04.86,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'll find as many as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:09.32,Main,,0,0,0,,So kiss me, Sis. You promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Milne...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:30.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:34.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this your little brother's?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:36.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:38.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I found it across the valley from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:42.73,Main,,0,0,0,,So I came to deliver it. Are you\Nthe one who threw it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:43.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:46.82,Main,,0,0,0,,But it belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:49.90,Main,,0,0,0,,If you forget what you've lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.24,Main,,0,0,0,,...you really will lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:02.33,Main,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.46,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:17.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I saw it happen. It was a complete\Naccident. An accidental death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:19.56,Main,,0,0,0,,As always,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:23.64,Main,,0,0,0,,he said he was going to give his\Nbeloved Princess Lulu some honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:29.36,Main,,0,0,0,,He went up to the bees' nest,\Nand he got stung and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:31.78,Main,,0,0,0,,It happened so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:35.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You promised! Kiss me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I hated you from the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:47.63,Main,,0,0,0,,...and I must have loved you\Nfrom the beginning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:19:00.35,Main,,0,0,0,,What a waste. Your honey porridge is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:07.15,Main,,0,0,0,,It's because I made her mad.\NI told her we were her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,And then she...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:13.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:20.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko... My love is about\Nmaking sure your love bears fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:27.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel like if I do that, I can see\Nhim again. Just one more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:29.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:31.80,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:36.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I have someplace to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:39.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:41.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Beyond the Wall of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:45.18,Main,,0,0,0,,To the human world?\NYou'll be killed if you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:48.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, because I got love from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:50.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You "got love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:53.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So I'm going to go return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:56.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll see her and deliver my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:20:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I promised we'd meet again, and we'd kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:02.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:05.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. A Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:10.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You promised! Kiss me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:12.50,Main,,0,0,0,,That girl is on the other side of the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:15.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm sure she's waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:19.93,Main,,0,0,0,,But she's human, right? If you go\Nmeet her, she might kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:23.56,Main,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:25.06,Main,,0,0,0,,That doesn't bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:28.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Nope, because I'm a criminal-bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:31.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't back down on my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.86,Main,,0,0,0,,--Take me along.\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:38.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Take me with you across the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:40.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll help you with your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:44.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I want you to get your Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:45.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:48.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Because... I'm a criminal-bear, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:59.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You're me before I lost mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:04.56,Main,,0,0,0,,No, you're not... I think\Nyou've already lost yours once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:08.52,Main,,0,0,0,,But if there's someone out there\Nstill alive for you to meet, we'll go--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:11.02,Main,,0,0,0,,even if she's across the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:17.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, defendant-bear Lulu Yurigasaki, I ask you:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:23.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you give up on love?\NOr will you give up on kisses?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:25.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't give up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll give up on kisses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:32.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. Please make me a human girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:36.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I really want to go to the other\Nside of the wall with Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:41.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You do realize that if you do that,\Nyou'll lose kisses forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:46.39,Main,,0,0,0,,My kisses are already lost.\NI can never see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:48.77,Main,,0,0,0,,But Ginko can still see hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:52.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I know she'll complete her\NPromise Kiss in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:55.32,Main,,0,0,0,,In other words, you are\Nentrusting Ginko Yurishiro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.32,0:21:59.36,Main,,0,0,0,,with the wish you couldn't fulfill?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:04.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Trying to achieve self-actualization\Nthat way is mere self-satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:07.49,Main,,0,0,0,,It's pride. It's a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:11.46,Main,,0,0,0,,That's fine. I'm a criminal-bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:15.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. I shall now declare the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:18.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:22.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:34.23,Main,,0,0,0,,And thus Princess Lulu--\Ncorrection, Lulu Yurigasaki--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.23,0:22:39.48,Main,,0,0,0,,set out with Ginko Yurishiro\Nto cross the Wall of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:46.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, the question remains:\NWill the Promise Kiss come to pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.45,0:22:50.24,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the sexy way. Shaba-da-doo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.78,0:23:31.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the boundary that severed{\i0}\N{\i1}ripe moon from sleeping forest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:38.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Break the law God shackles us with and smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:45.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I turned away from the bleating flock{\i0}\N{\i1}of shadows and howled my bloodthirsty ego{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here amidst the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.10,0:23:55.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Overflowing honey and soul{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.48,0:23:58.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to rend silk with my fangs{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:05.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm afraid you'll vanish{\i0}\N{\i1}like the world's last ray of hope{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.99,0:24:12.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The savage beast inside me{\i0}\N{\i1}tore out the throat of innocence{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:22.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, shoot me through the heart{\i0}\N{\i1}with your sweet-scented Barrett of love{\i0}
